dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Bayfield County, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and right of way (ROW) for Bayfield County in 2022 and includes the layers 'BAYFIELD_ROADS_2022' and 'BAYFIELD_ROW_2022'. [Roads: This layer contains road centerline data in Bayfield County. ROW: This layer contains ROW polyline data for right-of-way areas in Bayfield County. Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://www.bayfieldcounty.wi.gov/892/GIS-Data-Access]
